{"tid":1215586,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何檢舉翻牆的中國網民？這招幫助他們找到回家的路｜Zi 字媒體","createTime":"2019-06-13T07:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:24:44.000Z","uid":1665,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3669d89c8da8eff66f4c2642e0338083808af7b6","tid":1215586,"uid":1665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:36:33.000Z","msg":"常常在臉書、YouTube 上看到各種從大陸翻牆過來的網友，發表各種侵略性的言論嗎？現在有方法可以「回敬」他們了，而且是 100% 合法的方式，利用中國的中央網信辦 (國家互聯網信息辦公室)，檢舉違法利用 VPN 等翻牆軟體過來的民眾，將留言截圖 (越多越好)，就可以請這些網民「回家」吃自己啦！<br />\n國家互聯網信息辦公室：<a href=\"http://www.12377.cn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.12377.cn%2F&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWAaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=0106f9fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.12377.cn/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-0&h=30091da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 點擊上方連結進入中央網信辦，點擊「違法和不良信息舉報入口」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-1&h=88b57acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 接著會有個舉報須知，大概看一下就好 XD 不過看完滑到最下面有個同意需要按一下才能繼續下一步。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-2&h=9a00d522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 舉報分類選擇「其它」類。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-3&h=22bcb247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 接著點擊「匿名用戶舉報」，舉報平台選擇「客戶端 APP」，將 APP 名稱打上，並將 APP 官方的網址也貼上，最後舉報內容填寫違反使用 VPN 等類似陳述即可，因為最重要的截圖，有越多截圖越好，點擊「請選擇附件」來上傳，最後輸入驗證碼後按下繼續舉報即可。另外，同樣重要的是，請將繁體字通通都轉成簡體字，繁轉簡傳送門<a href=\"http://www.j4.com.tw/big-gb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.j4.com.tw%2Fbig-gb%2F&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWAaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=564ce14b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.j4.com.tw/big-gb/</a>也準備好啦～舉報成功後會收到一組查詢碼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-4&h=bf6b8afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 未來可以在同一個平台上查詢舉報處理進度！是不是覺得很新奇 XD 大家如果遇到翻牆網民來挑釁，就用這招回敬吧！學起來了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n國家互聯網信息辦公室：<a href=\"http://www.12377.cn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.12377.cn%2F&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWAaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=0106f9fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.12377.cn/</a><br />\n<br />\nsource : <a href=\"https://zi.media/@hugo3c/post/wUUnmQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzi.media%2F%40hugo3c%2Fpost%2FwUUnmQ&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWAaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=a5b08967\" target=\"_blank\">https://zi.media/@hugo3c/post/wUUnmQ</a>字媒體"},{"pid":"f473506fd8de9cfc72320eb2f210164f012e3c2b","tid":1215586,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d25118d03f405b09d46b462895ff3a3cee93aa4","tid":1215586,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}